After being inundated with calls to venture into gospel music, Kelly Khumalo has opened the floor to her fans. There is no doubt that Kelly has a powerful voice and can master practically any genre of music, however fans believe she's meant to do gospel music. The songstress left her heart on stage when she sang an emotional tribute to her friend, Akhumzi Jezile earlier this week. In a video shared on Instagram, Kelly said she received numerous messages encouraging her to release a gospel single, but she was still undecided about venturing into the genre. Kelly said she wanted to hear what her fans thought about the idea. Well, Kelly we're definitely here for it!